<p>
    This page provides an overview of the cultural landscape in the North East.
    In the first instance, it is limited to the Newcastle upon Tyne Local Authority area.
</p>

<p>
    The organisation list has been extracted from various sources of funding data which
    are published with an open license.
</p>

